"""
PART II Entitlement and amount

7A. Limitation of savings credit for certain mixed-age couples

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-21.

A person who is a member of a mixed-age couple, is not entitled to a savings credit unless one of the members of the couple—

(b)

remained entitled to a savings credit at all times since the beginning of 6th April 2016.
"""

savings_credit_section_7A_b_applies_person_is_member_of_mixed_age_couple:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

savings_credit_section_7A_b_one_member_remained_entitled_at_all_times_since_beginning_of_6th_april_2016:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

savings_credit_entitled_under_section_7A_b:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean
    from 2025-03-21:
        if savings_credit_section_7A_b_applies_person_is_member_of_mixed_age_couple:
            savings_credit_section_7A_b_one_member_remained_entitled_at_all_times_since_beginning_of_6th_april_2016
        else:
            true
